def visualize(orignal,augmented):
    fig = plt.figure()
    plt.subplot(1,2,1)
    plt.title('Original')
    plt.imshow(orignal)
    plt.subplot(1,2,2)
    plt.title('Augmented')
    plt.imshow(augmented)
